{"tid":2284187,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"1個人做不好！EXID約滿單飛　她「慘淪打工仔」曝辛酸","createTime":"2020-11-13T05:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T07:02:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f29f82211698520348bc5a726fd41daf582fa0df","tid":2284187,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:59:25.000Z","msg":"韓國MBN電視台的綜藝節目《Miss Back》邀請因長期沒有活動、逐漸被人淡忘的女偶像參加，其中T-ara前成員素妍因故退出，改由EXID的慧潾替補，昨（12）日她首度出場，分享了自己在EXID單飛後所面臨的困境，感嘆少了團員的分擔，很多事情一個人根本無法做好，還曾為了調整作息，開啟了打工的生活。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/17/1740673-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F17%2F1740673-PH.jpg&h=df209fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲EXID去年約滿宣布單飛不解散。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\nEXID在2012年出道，但起初星運並不順利，沒多久就面臨多位成員退出，活動難以進行，後來慧潾和率智加入，2014年因成員哈妮（Hani）跳《Up &amp; Down》的影片爆紅，EXID地位瞬間拉拔到一線女團，但去年5月EXID與經紀公司合約到期，全員陸續分道揚鑣，並宣布單飛不解散。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/13/2878928-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F13%2F2878928-PH.jpg&h=b54afb2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲慧潾參加《Miss Back》。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n昨晚慧潾首度在《Miss Back》中登場，提起接下節目的原因，她坦言，在團員各自單飛之後，大家都忙於個人的工作，「比起5個人一起活動的時候，現在有更多的煩惱」，希望可以以「歌手慧潾」的身分獲得成長，才會點頭加入，加上自己性格容易緊張，少了能夠一起分擔的團員，也讓她壓力加倍，認為總是無法一個人做好事情，也希望透過節目讓她克服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/13/2878926-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F13%2F2878926-PH.jpg&h=e73cd02c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲慧潾為了規律生活開啟打工生活。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n慧潾還透露，在跟公司的合約到期之後，因為沒了約束，生活自然變得怠惰，為了強迫自己早起，她在家附近找了一間餐廳，開啟了打工的生活，作息才逐漸變得規律。"},{"pid":"0981e3f597db45a611a263b4e6874cf2ba47dc3b","tid":2284187,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"做女團唔係打工咩  屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到好似做空姐唔係侍應咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e73a89020de7823b776e5707afd1ad483f26aa5","tid":2284187,"uid":68678,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"hyerin 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e7d9c136d6f9acc260c2283b2ea61f0b487714","tid":2284187,"uid":308570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:26:25.000Z","msg":"牙隱單飛之後應該都冇人記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1fab053e8fbf48cee809f2a8e51e20eb434b7b","tid":2284187,"uid":168319,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"係咪得我一個覺得佢入眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過好似整過頭"},{"pid":"00760d6ca5697370e58459426e9896e36388d17b","tid":2284187,"uid":27597,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T00:49:39.000Z","msg":"佢整容整到咁點會紅呀<br />\n唱歌又唔係特別好聽<br />\n綜藝能力麻麻<br />\n其實佢都係燉腳嫁咋果時"},{"pid":"60fca36db1077b827d3054740a8501a97c5af512","tid":2284187,"uid":15558,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T00:58:21.000Z","msg":"覺得佢整得特別醜<br />\n<br />\n整到非常礙眼嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420a7620d6e97c83bf9786c5c40610844da8ab2c","tid":2284187,"uid":8795,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T01:28:45.000Z","msg":"佢本身有樓有車 去打工都係為咗作息定時<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adfa9d0744641aa3b34ec477d7cc34ac0d8d400","tid":2284187,"uid":320858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T01:33:29.000Z","msg":"LE應該作首歌俾佢"},{"pid":"ba752f866ebb73a7675d158cdc3e4cd1dc58fb5d","tid":2284187,"uid":186755,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T01:35:26.000Z","msg":"靚又唔夠Hani靚<br />\n跳舞又唔夠正花跳得<br />\n唱又唔夠率智唱得<br />\nrap又唔夠LE rap得<br />\n<br />\n真係唔